预先告知感到困惑。 泽连斯基说，他「数次被惊到」。他说：「除了美国决定本身，第二个意外无疑就是，我是通过媒体报道才知道这件事的。」 泽连斯基还强调：「战略伙伴之间的关系应该是直接的。」（编译 / 钟忠）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-727a5c9e1fa2a0489d2fe96f466b89cd_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/464060123"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5JzJ/ff28tUsEAMaCDY1NDAzOTIyIK2rgYYGMCA47QVALXIJNDY0MDYwMTIzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1623341547.806042", "card_id": "Q_464147867", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 104}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待萨尔瓦多成为全球首个，以比特币作为法定货币国家，将对国际货币市场带来哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "路透社报道，萨尔瓦多 8 日以 62/84 的绝对多数通过立法，成为全球首个采用比特币作为法定货币的国家。萨尔瓦多总统布克勒称赞比特币的作用，称它有可能帮助居住在国外的萨尔瓦多人汇款回国，同时表示美元也将继续作为法定货币。 布克勒补充说，比特币的使用是可选的，不会给用户带来风险。该法案将在 90 天内成为法律，「创造了历史」。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-5e143ef9b0cecd166abea05e354e06fa_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/464147867"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5JzJ/ff28tUsEAMaCDY1NDIzNDM5ILGIg4YGMAs4rgNALnIJNDY0MTQ3ODY3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1623341547.8067439", "card_id": "Q_464058857", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 378}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "高考场外父亲举牌「不管考的怎么样，爸爸妈妈都很爱你」，当孩子面对压力和挑战时，什么才是最好的鼓励？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f0980e9a05072e7683b4aef0838d15b4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "28 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/464058857"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I5JzJ/ff28tUsEAMaCDY1NDAzNjQzIPGngYYGMDE41AdAL3IJNDY0MDU4ODU3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_l